## 3. Ads Integration ⚠️ NEW — NOT YET BUILT

> You want ads to show **while Gemini is processing** (the loading screen between scan submission and results).

### 🔴 CRITICAL — Set Up AdMob Account

1. Go to [admob.google.com](https://admob.google.com)
2. Create account → Add app → Platform: Android
3. Package name: `com.norla.app`
4. Create an **Interstitial Ad Unit** (full-screen ad during loading)
5. Note your **App ID** and **Ad Unit ID**

### 🔴 CRITICAL — Integrate Ads in Scan Processing Page

The ad should appear on the **scan processing/loading screen** (`src/app/(app)/scan/[id]/processing/page.tsx` or similar).

**Implementation approach:**
- Use **Google AdMob Interstitial** via `@capacitor-community/admob` plugin
- Show the interstitial ad WHILE Gemini processes (15-25 seconds is plenty for an ad)
- Dismiss ad when results are ready
- If ad fails to load, skip silently (don't block the user)

Files to create/modify:
| File | Action |
|------|--------|
| `package.json` | Add `@capacitor-community/admob` |
| `capacitor.config.ts` | Add AdMob plugin config with App ID |
| `android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml` | Add AdMob meta-data tag |
| New: `src/lib/admob.ts` | AdMob wrapper (init, show interstitial) |
| `src/app/(app)/scan/new/page.tsx` | Show interstitial after scan submit |

### 🟡 IMPORTANT — Ad Placement Strategy

| Placement | Type | When |
|-----------|------|------|
| **Scan processing** | Interstitial (full screen) | While Gemini AI processes (primary revenue) |
| History page (optional) | Banner (bottom) | When scrolling past results |
| Results page (optional) | Native/Banner | Below recommendations |

